---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Blog">
  <div class="page">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <div class="margin-bottom-3">
      <p class="color-neutral-200 font-size-1-125 line-height-1-6 margin-bottom-1">
        Welcome to my blog! This is where I share insights, tutorials, and
        thoughts on web development, design, and technology. I write about
        modern frameworks, best practices, and the evolving landscape of
        software development.
      </p>
      <p class="color-neutral-200 font-size-1-125 line-height-1-6 margin-bottom-1">
        I'm currently setting up the blog infrastructure and preparing my first
        posts. Stay tuned for content covering topics like:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="margin-bottom-4">
      <h2 class="margin-bottom-2 color-neutral-100">Upcoming Topics</h2>
      <div class="grid auto-fit-300 gap-2">
        <div class="card-topic">
          <h3>Astro & Modern Web Development</h3>
          <p>
            Deep dives into Astro's capabilities, performance optimizations, and
            building fast, content-focused websites.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-topic">
          <h3>Web Components with Lit</h3>
          <p>
            Practical guides for building reusable, framework-agnostic
            components using LitElement and modern web standards.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-topic">
          <h3>Design Systems & CSS Architecture</h3>
          <p>
            Building scalable design systems, CSS methodologies, and maintaining
            consistency across large projects.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-topic">
          <h3>Performance & Accessibility</h3>
          <p>
            Techniques for optimizing web performance and creating inclusive,
            accessible user experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-topic">
          <h3>Hosting & Deployment</h3>
          <p>
            Modern deployment strategies, cloud hosting solutions, and
            performance monitoring best practices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-topic">
          <h3>Developer Experience</h3>
          <p>
            Tools, workflows, and techniques that improve productivity and code
            quality in modern development environments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-align-center padding-1-5 card-surface">
      <h2 class="margin-bottom-1 color-neutral-100">Stay Updated</h2>
      <p class="color-neutral-200 margin-bottom-2 max-width-56 margin-auto">
        Want to be notified when I publish new posts? I'm planning to share
        valuable insights and practical tutorials that will help you build
        better web experiences.
      </p>
      <contact-component
        href="https://calendar.app.google/t9p2HfknyNWf1RNV6"
        text="Get in Touch for Updates"></contact-component>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>



<script>
  import "../components/contact";
</script>
